default2.1.
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThere is emerging evidence that eye care services are unable to meet current demand and will not meet rising demand in the future without significant improvements.
default 
default&#xa0;
default2.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultA recent survey found that half of all hospital eye units in England were unable to treat AMD patients within the recommended waiting times that would mini
defaultmise their risk of sight loss
default.
